metadata.name: F by PhutureMusic
metadata.description: Unlock the untold stories of birch sap smugglers with PhutureMusic Video NFT. Follow their daring journey through time as they reenact the original PhutureMusic "F" track from the upcoming "Hotel Earth" album. Experience the thrill of discovering a secret life and groove along to the rhythm of music in this unique & captivating video. Get it now and join the wild adventure!
